        },
        {
            "title": "中東衝突嚇崩市場，多個股市停牌！美指期貨齊跌，布油兩日升超12%，比特幣突破7萬美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周三，3月4日，中東地緣衝突持續升級，此前升勢強勁的亞太市場大幅回檔，韓國股市今日一度暴跌超12.5%觸發熔斷，創史上最大單日跌幅，泰股暴跌8%觸發停牌。阿聯酋股市停牌兩日後重挫，迪拜股指盤中跌近5%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美股開市前，CBOE Volatility Index升近5%，美股指期貨集體下跌，納指100期貨跌近百點，跌幅達0.39%，道指30期貨跌166點，跌幅達0.34%，標普500期貨跌0.25%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3c5ef269-596a-3d86-bbda-f087202cedfe-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"199\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RiSWQ7w7OmbJHgdydw5zBA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTE5OQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/44aade117c8fbb7ca43ad9443036a4b4\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">XAU/USD升近2%報5180美元，XAG/USD升4.5%至85美元。霍爾木茲海峽航運中斷，原油繼續拉升3%，WTI原油期貨現報76.9美元，倫敦布倫特原油期貨突破84.1美元，兩日內累計上升約12%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"668\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NxWh0c4.BpRJBfnniXTp.Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTExMTc-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/e56c737646836f7cc7f7d3cf888d37f3\" width=\"574\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元指數升0.02%，現報99.08。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"577\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rDo7kQC6mFiuEbkSqp2T0A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/7738b9690ec4d7c2c108ff4a7a740dab\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">比特幣 (BitfinexUSD)直線拉升升超5.5%，突破7萬美元大關。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"582\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mlYpOSTyWZD0x4pxFnNl7g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/23b365f089c6d6ab274ee9ef4fe5d368\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><u><span>3</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>月</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>AI</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>精選股已上線，中東局勢擾動全球，</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>AI</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>助您跑贏市場，</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>InvestingPro</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>立享</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>50%</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>折扣，</span></u></strong> <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em><span>即刻點擊訂閱</span></em></strong></a><strong><u><span>！</span></u></strong></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"472\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CURKT.9MXPa.OofIyeLBkA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ3Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/71ae5090b14d5d395cc490c1cbce8740\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><span><br/></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><br/><br/><br/><br/></p></blockquote></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E6%9D%B1%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E5%9A%87%E5%B4%A9%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-%E5%A4%9A%E5%80%8B%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E5%81%9C%E7%89%8C-%E7%BE%8E%E6%8C%87%E6%9C%9F%E8%B2%A8%E9%BD%8A%E8%B7%8C-%E5%B8%83%E6%B2%B9%E5%85%A9%E6%97%A5%E5%8D%87%E8%B6%8512-%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B9%A3%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B47%E8%90%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-101718541.html",
